  m_text: "Win: Play continues until a player reaches 7 points (normal) or 3 points
    (Sudden Win). \n\r\nNormal Mode: At 7 points a winner is declared. Play continues
    for one additional round to allow the current judge to get an even amount of
    play rounds. If a tie is not reached, the game ends with the winner declared.
    In the case of a tie, an additional round is played to break the tie.\r\n\r\nSudden
    Win: Extra booster rockets have accelerated the journey to Psyche 16. First player
    to 3 points, regardless of ties or rounds played wins."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
